               <p>(The prisoner put in a written defence, expressing his contition for hav<lb></lb>ing pledged the articles, but that it was his intention to redeem them, as the prosecutor owed him 3<hi rend="italic">l</hi>. 12<hi rend="italic">s</hi>.)</p>
